OL,3,CMan who stabbed neighbour to death
OL,4,Cabsconds from mental health facility
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his neighbour to
OL,7,Fdeath in 2004 has absconded from a
OL,8,Fmental health facility in east London,
OL,9,Fsparking a police appeal.
OL,11,FPhilip Theophilou, 54, left the
OL,12,Ffacility in Homerton on Sunday and has
OL,13,Fnot returned, the Metropolitan Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
