OL,3,CMan who stabbed neighbour to death
OL,4,Cabsconds from mental health facility
OL,6,FTheophilou admitted manslaughter on
OL,7,Fthe grounds of diminished
OL,8,Fresponsibility after killing Simon
OL,9,FBreed, 51, in a knife attack, then
OL,10,Fliving rough in Hyde Park for three
OL,11,Fdays before he was caught, the Old
OL,12,FBailey heard in 2005.
OL,14,FMr Breed received six stab wounds and
OL,15,Fseveral defence wounds, after
OL,16,FTheophilou lay in wait for him with a
OL,17,Fkitchen knife outside their house in
OL,18,FCornwall Avenue, Alexandra Park.
