OL,3,CMan who stabbed neighbour to death
OL,4,Cabsconds from mental health facility
OL,6,FTheophilou ran to the park from his
OL,7,Fhome in north London, leaving Mr Breed
OL,8,Fdying outside his house.
OL,10,FHe was sent to Broadmoor special
OL,11,Fhospital without limit of time under
OL,12,Fthe Mental Health Act, in November
OL,13,F2005.
OL,15,FDoctors said he suffered from
OL,16,Fschizophrenia but had not been taking
OL,17,Fhis medication at the time of the
OL,18,Fkilling in April 2004.
