OL,6,FPolice believe he travelled to the
OL,7,FGreen Park area on Sunday at about
OL,8,F11.25am.
OL,10,FHe was wearing a grey jumper, blue
OL,11,Fjeans, and a black jacket.
OL,13,FOfficers and medical professionals are
OL,14,Fconcerned at his lack of access to
OL,15,Fmedication and the risk he may pose
OL,16,Fwithout it.
OL,18,FTheophilou had caused thousands of
OL,19,Fpounds worth of damage to Mr Breed's
OL,20,Fhouse and car with a meat cleaver in
OL,21,FJanuary 2003.
