OL,3,CMan who stabbed neighbour to death
OL,4,Cabsconds from mental health facility
OL,6,FThe attack followed building work
OL,7,Fstarted by Mr Breed shortly after he
OL,8,Fmoved in 2002, and which had caused a
OL,9,Fcrack in the next door house that
OL,10,FTheophilou shared with his parents,
OL,11,Fthe court heard.
OL,13,FHe was sectioned under the Mental
OL,14,FHealth Act and released from St Ann's
OL,15,FHospital in August 2003.
OL,17,FThere were no problems until eight
OL,18,Fmonths later when Mr Breed was
OL,19,Fattacked at night as he returned from
OL,20,Fplaying at a folk club.
