OL,4,Cabsconds from mental health facility
OL,6,FPaul Brogan, defending, said
OL,7,FTheophilou had been discharged from
OL,8,Fhospital in 2003 in apparently
OL,9,F"unsatisfactory circumstances".
OL,11,F"There was a failure to monitor or
OL,12,Ftreat him after discharge," said Mr
OL,13,FBrogan.
OL,15,FAnyone who sees Theophilou should not
OL,16,Fapproach him. Instead, call 999
OL,17,Fimmediately quoting CAD 3598/31Mar.
